eNCA's Nceba Ntlanganiso has the details. #eNCA #DStv403  JOHANNESBURG - Nelson Mandela Bay mayor, Eugene Johnson has led a public water awareness campaign in Gqeberha. She and a team from the municipality went out in the early hours of the morning targeting major traffic intersections, and spreading the word about saving water. eNCA's Nceba Ntlanganiso has the details in the video above.